Package no.brunostengine

Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
no.brunostengine.GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
PoolableObject
public class GameObject extends Object
Represent any object meant to be present within a scene, whether visible or in the background. This class allows for flexibility through its use of the Component class.
